dct_title_s: Delaware River Front of Salem County
dct_description_sm: Sheet 1: Map covers area from Oldmans Creek to Penns Neck. Map depicts low/high water lines: lines of 6 feet in blue and lines of 12 feet in green. Map also includes Bradways Creek and Bout Creek.
Sheet 2: Map covers area from Penns Neck on North to Hope Creek on South. Map depicts high/low water lines of the Delaware River: lines of 6 feet in blue and lines of 12 feet in green.

Sheet 3: Map covers area from Stony Point to Stow Creek along the Delaware River. Map depicts high/low water lines of the Delaware River: lines of 6 feet in blue and lines of 12 feet in green.Map includes Stow Creek, Stony Inlet, and Hope Creek.
